    "date": "2020-07-02T20:36:03Z",
    "text": "Climate Readiness Act of 2020\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Defense to report on (1) the national security implications associated with climate change, and (2) strategies and approaches to responding to such change. The report must consider geopolitical and military impacts, including effects on the resiliency of missions of the Armed Forces."
